parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended activation of the automatic braking system can cause the vehicle to suddenly stop, potentially leading to accidents or rear-end collisions, especially if there are vehicles behind.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly stops or slows down without warning
the "BRAKE" warning light illuminates on the dashboard
and the seatbelt may lock or tighten.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The false forward collision warnings can cause driver distraction, confusion, and potentially lead to accidents or incorrect braking.
symptoms: The "BRAKE" warning light illuminates on the dashboard
and the vehicle may emit a loud beeping sound
even when there are no vehicles or objects in front of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system failures can cause a range of issues, including loss of vehicle functionality, distraction, and safety risks.
symptoms: Display screen goes blank
navigation head unit becomes erratic
cabin smells like gasoline
and strange noises from the AVAS acoustic vehicle alert system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Spontaneous shattering or cracking of the sunroof or windshield can cause safety risks, including injury from flying glass and reduced visibility.
symptoms: Sunroof explodes or shatters without warning
windshield cracks or shatters without apparent cause.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Vehicle Stalling and Loss of Power
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Vehicle stalling or loss of power can cause accidents, especially on highways, and leave drivers stranded.
symptoms: Vehicle stalls or loses power
check engine light blinks
and pressing the accelerator does not provide power to the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Malfunctioning door locks and actuators can cause safety risks, including the inability to lock doors and potential for unauthorized access.
symptoms: Door lock actuator fails
door locks do not engage
and clicking sounds are heard when attempting to lock doors.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Battery drain and charging issues can cause inconvenience, safety risks, and reduced vehicle functionality.
symptoms: Vehicle battery drains when parked for extended periods
and the battery needs to be boosted to start the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Malfunctioning safety and security features can cause safety risks, including unauthorized access and distraction.
symptoms: Key fob feature causes windows to roll down and moon roof to open unintentionally
and no warning or alerts are provided.
